## 🛠️ DevOps Hardening & CI/CD Pipelines

-   **`Dockerfile`**: A high-performance, multi-stage Docker build optimized for Hugging Face Spaces free container environments. Pre-seeds 3,000 baseline biometric rows inside the SQLite offline store during the build stage to eliminate initialization cold starts.
-   **`.github/workflows/vital-core-pipeline.yml`**: Full GitHub Actions workflow executing code formatting checks (Black), Python syntax checks (Flake8), automated unit/integration test suites (Pytest), and local container build verification.

